**Explanation**

The `@Jacksonized` annotation is, unfortunately, prioritized over the explicitly registered custom deserializer so Jackson is trying to use `Person.PersonBuilder` for the deserialization instead of 
`PersonDeserializer`. Seems like a bug in Jackson so I&#39;ve opened [#3901](https://github.com/FasterXML/jackson-databind/issues/3901).

